'''FNV-23''', known also as the '''Gray Death''', was an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]]-created virus first tested on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Sedesia]]. Developed under the auspices of the [[Pathogen-Based Loyalty Enhancement Program]] by [[Doctor/Legends|Doctor]] [[Fesjo Negleem]], this virus had the property of continually changing its antigen needs, making it impossible for an individual to become immune to it as well as making it virtually impossible to cure.

